@startuml
hide empty description

[*] --> PlantSelected : User selects plant from collection

PlantSelected --> AwaitingLocation : Plant has no stored location [Flow 3a]
PlantSelected --> AwaitingGPS : Plant has location / GPS unavailable [Flow 4a]
PlantSelected --> Navigating : Plant has location / GPS available

AwaitingLocation --> AwaitingGPS : User sets location / GPS unavailable [Flow 4a]
AwaitingLocation --> Navigating : User sets location / GPS available

AwaitingGPS --> Navigating : User enables location services

state Navigating {
  [*] --> UpdatingPosition
  UpdatingPosition --> WeakSignal : GPS signal degrades [Flow 7a]
  WeakSignal --> UpdatingPosition : GPS signal restored
}

Navigating --> PlantSelected : User selects different plant [Flow 7b]
Navigating --> ProximityReached : Distance drops below threshold

ProximityReached --> NeedsMoreDetails : User cannot locate exact plant [Flow 8a]
NeedsMoreDetails --> Arrived : User finds plant after viewing details
ProximityReached --> Arrived : User finds plant directly

Arrived --> [*] : Plant detail/care page displayed

@enduml
